---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What ages/levels of experience do you work with?",
    answer:
      "Any age or level of experience is welcome. You can be new to working out or a seasoned veteran, I can adapt your program to fit your needs.",
  },
  {
    question:
      "I have a special condition (arthritis, osteoporosis, bunions, ect), or am recovering from an injury or operation (heart surgery, joint injury, car crash, ect), can TWR Fitness help?",
    answer:
      "Yes BUT, it is necessary that your doctor clears you to come train with me. I can work alongside physical therapists and as a certified personal trainer I am educated on how training can benefit people in a variety of situations. I also always research my client’s conditions to make sure I am providing to them exactly what they need to improve.",
  },
  {
    question: "What are Tristan’s certifications?",
    answer:
      "I am certified through the Academy of Sports Medicine as a Personal Trainer. I am currently working to complete the Corrective Exercise Specialist Course. I am also CPR and AED certified through the Red Cross. ",
  },
  {
    question: "What is Tristan’s level of experience?",
    answer:
      "I started out as a client of Master Trainer Kyle Crocker of CalisFit in Connecticut. Kyle helped me with longstanding complex health problems and then offered me a mentorship. Under him I learned for two years while also starting my company. I have been training for 4 years now and have worked with people across all levels of age, condition, and goals. I am constantly reading up on the newest research while working towards new specialist certifications and still go to my original mentor for advice and to talk shop.",
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-bg px-edge py-10 lg:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <h2
          class="font-oswald text-5xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight text-text-dark"
        >
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
          Can’t find the answer you’re looking for? Visit our <a
            href="/contact"
            class="font-semibold text-primary">contact page</a
          > and reach out.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 lg:col-span-7 lg:mt-0">
        <dl class="space-y-10">
          {
            faqs.map((faq) => (
              <div>
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                  {faq.question}
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                  {faq.answer}
                </dd>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
